# PWA: Connection Lost Only

The PWA should **only** be used to show that the user has lost connection to the website.

## Do
- Show a "You've lost connection" banner when `navigator.onLine` is false
- Serve a minimal offline fallback page when navigation fails due to no network
- Cache only the static offline.html page in the service worker

## Don't
- Cache app pages or content for offline browsing
- Add push notifications
- Add background sync
- Use the PWA for installability/standalone app features beyond the connection UI
